// Suggestion: Enable strict mode by setting `"strict": true` in the `compilerOptions`. Consider specifying `"moduleResolution": "node"` and `"esModuleInterop": true` for better compatibility with ES modules.
{
    "compilerOptions": {
        "strict": true,
        "target": "esnext",
        "esModuleInterop": true
    },
    "include": ["src/**/*.ts"],
    "extends": "./src/config/root.json",
    "exclude": ["package", "node_modules", "examples"]
}
